        <div class="image-options">
            <label style="display:inline-block;margin-right:8px;cursor:pointer;">
                <input onfocusout="saveanswer('Opgave 1a svar', 'AnswerBox1')" type="radio" id="AnswerBox1" name="Answer1a" value="correct" style="display:none;" />
                <img src="~/Img/Opgave1/eddikesyre.png" alt="Eddikesyre 1" style="width:150px;height:150px;border:2px solid transparent;object-fit:contain;" onclick="selectImage('AnswerBox1', this)" />
            </label>
            <label style="display:inline-block;margin-right:8px;cursor:pointer;">
                <input onfocusout="saveanswer('Opgave 1a svar', 'AnswerBox2')" type="radio" id="AnswerBox2" name="Answer1a" value="incorrect" style="display:none;" />
                <img src="~/Img/Opgave1/eddikesyre2.png" alt="Option 2" style="width:150px;height:150px;border:2px solid transparent;object-fit:contain;" onclick="selectImage('AnswerBox2', this)" />
            </label>
            <label style="display:inline-block;cursor:pointer;">
                <input onfocusout="saveanswer('Opgave 1a svar', 'AnswerBox3')" type="radio" id="AnswerBox3" name="Answer1a" value="incorrect" style="display:none;" />
                <img src="~/Img/Opgave1/eddikesyre3.png" alt="Option 3" style="width:150px;height:150px;border:2px solid transparent;object-fit:contain;" onclick="selectImage('AnswerBox3', this)" />
            </label>
            <noscript>
                <div>
                    <input onfocusout="saveanswer('Opgave 1a svar', 'AnswerBox1_nojs')" type="radio" id="AnswerBox1_nojs" name="Answer1a_nojs" value="Eddike1" /> Eddikesyre 1
                </div>
                <div>
                    <input onfocusout="saveanswer('Opgave 1a svar', 'AnswerBox2_nojs')" type="radio" id="AnswerBox2_nojs" name="Answer1a_nojs" value="incorrect" /> Option 2
                </div>
                <div>
                    <input onfocusout="saveanswer('Opgave 1a svar', 'AnswerBox3_nojs')" type="radio" id="AnswerBox3_nojs" name="Answer1a_nojs" value="incorrect" /> Option 3
                </div>
            </noscript>
        </div>

        <p>1b. Hvorfor kan man også kalde eddikesyre for ethansyre?</p>
            <input onfocusout="saveanswer('Opgave 1b svar', 'AnswerBox1')" type="radio" id="AnswerBox1" name="Answer1" value="ethan-gruppe" >Molekylet består af en ethan-gruppe (C-C), med en carboxyl-gruppe (COOH).
Når en carboxyl-gruppe er bundet til et alkan navngives stoffen ”alkan+syre”, hvis i dette tilfælde er ”ethan + syre" </input>
            <br />
            <input onfocusout="saveanswer('Opgave 1b svar', 'AnswerBox1')" type="radio" id="AnswerBox1" name="Answer1" value ="incorrect">Når molekylet består af en ethan-gruppe (C-C), har det et lige antal af C og O molekyler
 </input>
            <br />
            <input onfocusout="saveanswer('Opgave 1b svar', 'AnswerBox1')" type="radio" id="AnswerBox1" name="Answer1" value ="incorrect" >Det kan man ikke, da det ikke er en carboxyl-gruppe</input>
